```{r pancreas 33177357, include=FALSE}

PMID_33177357 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('33177357', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_33177357 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_33177357$eprint)

doi_33177357 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_33177357$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)
```
